If
.I n
is not supplied, the current page width (set with the
.FONT CB ".PAGE SIZE"
command) is used.
.
.
.TP
.FONT CB ".PAPER SIZE" I " n" CB , I m
.TP
.FONT CB ".PAGE SIZE" I " n" CB , I m
.TP
.FONT CB ".PS" I " n" CB , I m
sets the size of the page
