This command allows normally typed text to be
.I justified
without special commands.
.
It does not cause a paragraph if
.I blank lines
are followed by a command.
.
.
.TP
.FONT CB .NOAUTOPARAGRAPH
.TQ
.FONT CB .NAP
disengages the
.FONT CI AUTOPARAGRAPH
mode.
.
.
