.I hyphenation
has not been disabled,
.FONT CB RNO
will attempt to
.I break
words which cause line overflow into syllables.)
.
.
.TP
.FONT CB .NOFILL
.TP
.FONT CB .NF
disengages the
.I fill
and
.IR "justify modes" .
