.FONT CB .FILL R ,
a single occurrance of
.FONT CB NOJUSTIFY
will cause the remainder of the file to be
.IR unjustified ,
with
.I filling
as specified.
.
In order to
.I justify
but
.I not fill
(not recommended), a
.FONT CB .JUSTIFY
command must follow every
.FONT CB .NOFILL
command.
.
.
.RE
.
.
.TP
.FONT CB ".UPPER CASE"
.TQ
.FONT CB .UC
sets the output mode to
